{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC10_MER_080.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x13,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "See, didn't I tell you? They're quite difficult to deal with."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You were right... I didn't expect it to be this much trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I think it's best to withdraw immediately before this gets any worse."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What happened?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well, you know how we had that Homunculus customer last time?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Homunculus...? Oh, the one who said he wanted sparkles...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes, that one. So I gathered up a bunch of jewels and had them delivered, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "They were returned today.<CR>Like, they returned everything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xb0,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I helped pick out the jewels, so I can guarantee their quality and value."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "So those jewels didn't meet Homunculus's expectations?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xfa,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "We don't know. Their words are just so abstract..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0xfb,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, this is what happened after we did all that we could. I think we should pull out from this order..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "No. Mr. Owner, please let me try one more time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, but my hunch is telling me that no matter what we do, we won't get a good result..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But your hunches are never right,<CR>so it'll be fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Plus, if we give up now, it'll hurt the reputation of this store!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, if you feel that strongly about it, we did receive the payment in advance..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Okay, let's try it one more time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Yes, sir. Okay, I'm getting pumped up now! Just you wait, Homunculus!"
        }
    ]
}